N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 13 ยง 80.16 - Issuer statement and other requirements

State Regulations

Nothing contained in these regulations shall exempt any issuer from compliance with
section
359-e
of
the General Business Law with respect to the filing of Issuer Statements, State Notices and Further State Notices or with respect to any other
provision of article 23-A. Notes
